What are the Variables

When we have to make computer to do something for us, we have to provide the computer
with instructions and data.To store this data we need something that can help us store and retrieve the information
when we need it
Variables will helps us to store this data

There are 8 Basic Types of variables in java.They are called as Primitive data Types
to store the numeric values
Byte
Short
int
long

to store the decimal values
float
double

to store true or false
boolean

to store the character values

char

String it is not data type
if you want store group of characters as single unit we are going to use the String
String is immutable class
String value1="7878asdfasd"
String  value2="1957495"


